data.description: Motivated seller! $5,000 towards closing costs or rate buy down! This beautiful 5-acre property features a 3 bed, 2 bath main home and two additional outbuildings for your hobbies or storage use!  Outbuildings are a potential in-law suite with kitchen and bath inside.  Natural light flows freely here! Master bedroom offers a walk-in closet and en suite bathroom. Kitchen boasts granite, black appliances, and built-ins for storage. Enjoy quiet on your screened in porch or relax in your large, beautiful living room for entertaining that looks out onto your peaceful property. Outbuildings sold AS-IS, but have electrical & plumbing run to them.
